text: Chung Jae-woong (born 2 June 1999) is a South Korean speed skater who competes internationally. He participated at the 2018 Winter Olympics, in men's 1000 metres. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:South Korean male speed skaters Category:Olympic speed skaters of South Korea Category:Speed skaters at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Competitors at the 2016 Winter Youth Olympics
